instruction: Make a list of practical items needed for a home office
output:
Practical items for a home office: 
1. Desk 
2. Chair 
3. Computer 
4. Printer 
5. Phone or VoIP headset 
6. Network accessories (router, switch, modem, etc.) 
7. File storage system 
8. Whiteboard or markers 
9. Office supplies (calendar, pen, paper, stapler, etc.) 
10. Plain white or neutral colored wall for a projector 
11. External hard drive 
12. Surge protector 
13. Clock 
14. Desk lamp 
15. Notepad and pen caddy 
16. Organization system (baskets, bins, etc.) 
17. Decorations (plants, artwork, etc.) 
18. Label maker 
19. Conferencing equipment (webcam, microphone, etc.)
